  "text": "In Section 3, a list of the isomorphism classes of the 6-dimensional nilpotent Lie algebras over an arbitrary field is given. The first part of this theorem concerning fields of characteristic different from 2 was already proved in the article [CITATION_1] by the second author (see also [CITATION_2] for more details).",
